title: Happy Jets
description: Cecilia dreams of starting a rosy life and finding with her handsome, wealthy prince on a white horse. Instead she gets rented a messy room by a shady guy and she even has to find out later, that the room is already owned by another girl, Jill. Thus, Cecilia's problems have just began.

matches.title: The Magical Revolution of the Reincarnated Princess and the Genius Young Lady
